{"color": "cyan", "emoji": "\ud83d\udee0\ufe0f", "event_type": "Command Finished", "message": "completed, exit 0: /bin/zsh -lc 'cat frontend/package.json'", "raw_event": {"item": {"aggregated_output": "{\n  \"name\": \"storyteller-frontend\",\n  \"private\": true,\n  \"version\": \"0.1.0\",\n  \"type\": \"module\",\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"dev\": \"vite\",\n    \"build\": \"tsc -b && vite build\",\n    \"lint\": \"eslint . --max-warnings=0\",\n    \"format\": \"prettier --write .\",\n    \"format:check\": \"prettier --check .\",\n    \"preview\": \"vite preview\",\n    \"test\": \"vitest run\"\n  },\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"react\": \"^19.2.4\",\n    \"react-dom\": \"^19.2.4\",\n    \"react-router-dom\": \"^7.13.2\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"@eslint/js\": \"^9.39.4\",\n    \"@testing-library/jest-dom\": \"^6.9.1\",\n    \"@testing-library/react\": \"^16.3.2\",\n    \"@types/node\": \"^24.12.0\",\n    \"@types/react\": \"^19.2.14\",\n    \"@types/react-dom\": \"^19.2.3\",\n    \"@vitejs/plugin-react\": \"^6.0.1\",\n    \"eslint\": \"^9.39.4\",\n    \"eslint-plugin-react-hooks\": \"^7.0.1\",\n    \"eslint-plugin-react-refresh\": \"^0.5.2\",\n    \"globals\": \"^17.4.0\",\n    \"jsdom\": \"^29.0.1\",\n    \"prettier\": \"^3.8.1\",\n    \"typescript\": \"~5.9.3\",\n    \"typescript-eslint\": \"^8.57.0\",\n    \"vite\": \"^8.0.1\",\n    \"vitest\": \"^4.1.2\"\n  }\n}\n", "command": "/bin/zsh -lc 'cat frontend/package.json'", "exit_code": 0, "id": "item_14", "status": "completed", "type": "command_execution"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 32, "prompt_index": 21, "prompt_name": "20 \u2014 Frontend App Shell and Routing", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T01:12:09-07:00"}
{"color": "cyan", "emoji": "\ud83d\udee0\ufe0f", "event_type": "Command Finished", "message": "completed, exit 0: /bin/zsh -lc \"sed -n '1,260p' frontend/src/styles/index.css\"", "raw_event": {"item": {"aggregated_output": ":root {\n  color: #182028;\n  background:\n    radial-gradient(\n      circle at top left,\n      rgba(245, 198, 140, 0.45),\n      transparent 34%\n    ),\n    radial-gradient(\n      circle at top right,\n      rgba(102, 129, 173, 0.38),\n      transparent 28%\n    ),\n    linear-gradient(180deg, #f4ede1 0%, #f9f5ef 42%, #eff2f7 100%);\n  font-family: 'Avenir Next', 'Trebuchet MS', 'Gill Sans', sans-serif;\n  font-synthesis: none;\n  line-height: 1.5;\n  text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;\n\n  --border-soft: rgba(35, 49, 64, 0.12);\n  --ink-deep: #182028;\n  --ink-soft: #4c5a66;\n  --panel: rgba(255, 252, 247, 0.88);\n  --panel-strong: rgba(255, 250, 242, 0.96);\n  --shadow: 0 28px 80px rgba(24, 32, 40, 0.14);\n  --brand-deep: #274464;\n  --brand-moss: #56765a;\n  --brand-gold: #b68043;\n}\n\n* {\n  box-sizing: border-box;\n}\n\nhtml {\n  min-height: 100%;\n}\n\nbody {\n  margin: 0;\n  min-height: 100vh;\n}\n\nbody,\n#root {\n  min-height: 100vh;\n}\n\nbutton,\ninput,\ntextarea,\nselect {\n  font: inherit;\n}\n\n.app-shell {\n  position: relative;\n  min-height: 100vh;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  padding: 32px 24px 56px;\n}\n\n.app-shell__glow {\n  position: absolute;\n  inset: auto;\n  width: 24rem;\n  height: 24rem;\n  border-radius: 999px;\n  filter: blur(36px);\n  opacity: 0.45;\n  pointer-events: none;\n  animation: drift 16s ease-in-out infinite;\n}\n\n.app-shell__glow--left {\n  top: -6rem;\n  left: -5rem;\n  background: rgba(182, 128, 67, 0.32);\n}\n\n.app-shell__glow--right {\n  right: -7rem;\n  bottom: -8rem;\n  background: rgba(74, 114, 162, 0.24);\n  animation-delay: -8s;\n}\n\n.app-header,\n.app-main {\n  position: relative;\n  z-index: 1;\n}\n\n.app-header {\n  width: min(1120px, 100%);\n  margin: 0 auto 28px;\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: end;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  gap: 20px;\n}\n\n.app-kicker,\n.eyebrow {\n  margin: 0;\n  font-size: 0.78rem;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  letter-spacing: 0.18em;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n}\n\n.app-kicker,\n.eyebrow {\n  color: var(--brand-gold);\n}\n\n.eyebrow-muted {\n  color: var(--brand-moss);\n}\n\n.app-brand,\nh1,\nh2,\nh3 {\n  font-family:\n    'Iowan Old Style', 'Palatino Linotype', 'Book Antiqua', Georgia, serif;\n  letter-spacing: -0.02em;\n}\n\n.app-brand {\n  display: block;\n  margin-top: 0.35rem;\n  font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.8rem);\n  color: var(--brand-deep);\n}\n\n.app-caption {\n  margin: 0;\n  max-width: 20rem;\n  text-align: right;\n  color: var(--ink-soft);\n}\n\n.app-main {\n  width: min(1120px, 100%);\n  margin: 0 auto;\n}\n\n.home-grid {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;\n  gap: 20px;\n}\n\n.panel {\n  position: relative;\n  padding: 24px;\n  border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);\n  border-radius: 28px;\n  background: var(--panel);\n  box-shadow: var(--shadow);\n  backdrop-filter: blur(14px);\n  animation: rise-in 700ms ease both;\n}\n\n.panel:nth-child(2) {\n  animation-delay: 90ms;\n}\n\n.panel:nth-child(3) {\n  animation-delay: 180ms;\n}\n\n.panel:nth-child(4) {\n  animation-delay: 270ms;\n}\n\n.panel-hero {\n  min-height: 22rem;\n  padding: 32px;\n  background:\n    linear-gradient(\n      140deg,\n      rgba(255, 250, 242, 0.96),\n      rgba(244, 238, 230, 0.9)\n    ),\n    var(--panel-strong);\n}\n\n.panel-hero h1 {\n  margin: 0.45rem 0 0.85rem;\n  font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 4.4rem);\n  color: var(--ink-deep);\n}\n\n.lede {\n  margin: 0 0 1rem;\n  max-width: 18ch;\n  font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.4vw, 1.45rem);\n  color: var(--brand-deep);\n}\n\n.body-copy,\n.panel-heading p,\n.session-item p {\n  margin: 0;\n  color: var(--ink-soft);\n}\n\n.tag-list,\n.session-list,\n.stage-list {\n  list-style: none;\n  padding: 0;\n  margin: 0;\n}\n\n.tag-list {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-wrap: wrap;\n  gap: 10px;\n  margin-top: 1.4rem;\n}\n\n.tag {\n  padding: 0.5rem 0.8rem;\n  border-radius: 999px;\n  background: rgba(39, 68, 100, 0.08);\n  color: var(--brand-deep);\n  font-size: 0.94rem;\n  font-weight: 600;\n}\n\n.panel-heading {\n  display: grid;\n  gap: 0.45rem;\n  margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\n}\n\n.panel-heading h2,\n.panel-status h2 {\n  margin: 0;\n  font-size: 1.6rem;\n  color: var(--ink-deep);\n}\n\n.session-list {\n  display: grid;\n  gap: 12px;\n}\n\n.session-item {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: start;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  gap: 14px;\n  padding: 16px 18px;\n  border-radius: 20px;\n  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.66);\n}\n", "command": "/bin/zsh -lc \"sed -n '1,260p' frontend/src/styles/index.css\"", "exit_code": 0, "id": "item_13", "status": "completed", "type": "command_execution"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 33, "prompt_index": 21, "prompt_name": "20 \u2014 Frontend App Shell and Routing", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T01:12:09-07:00"}
{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "I\u2019ve isolated the current frontend to a single decorative home route plus a backend ping hook. I\u2019m now turning that into a routeable app shell with explicit extension points: page modules, shared UI, API utilities, and state-store placeh...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_15", "text": "I\u2019ve isolated the current frontend to a single decorative home route plus a backend ping hook. I\u2019m now turning that into a routeable app shell with explicit extension points: page modules, shared UI, API utilities, and state-store placeholders, with tests built around memory routing instead of the old single-component assertions.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 34, "prompt_index": 21, "prompt_name": "20 \u2014 Frontend App Shell and Routing", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T01:12:29-07:00"}
