{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "The first browser check exposed a Compose quirk: `docker compose run` wants to recreate the `backend` dependency, so parallel QA runs collide on container names. I\u2019m switching to a single-browser-container flow now, which is the safer pa...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_57", "text": "The first browser check exposed a Compose quirk: `docker compose run` wants to recreate the `backend` dependency, so parallel QA runs collide on container names. I\u2019m switching to a single-browser-container flow now, which is the safer path in this repo, and then I\u2019ll run the three specs sequentially.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 107, "prompt_index": 21, "prompt_name": "20 \u2014 Frontend App Shell and Routing", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T01:21:16-07:00"}
