{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "Implemented the frontend app shell and routing for prompt 20 and wrote the required reviewer summary at [20-frontend-app-shell-and-routing.summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/prompts/20-frontend-app-shell-and-routing.summary.md). T...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_89", "text": "Implemented the frontend app shell and routing for prompt 20 and wrote the required reviewer summary at [20-frontend-app-shell-and-routing.summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/prompts/20-frontend-app-shell-and-routing.summary.md).\n\nThe frontend now has a real routed shell with `/`, `/sessions/:sessionId`, and a not-found fallback, plus a global header, connection indicator, toast dock placeholder, and the new `pages/`, `api/`, `hooks/`, `shared/ui/`, and `state/` structure. I also added route tests and browser QA specs, then verified with `npm run test`, `npm run lint`, `npm run format:check`, `npm run build`, and Puppeteer route checks that produced:\n- `.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-20-home-route.png`\n- `.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-20-session-route.png`\n- `.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-20-not-found-route.png`\n\nCheckpoint commit: `eb6fd69` (`feat(prompt-20): frontend app shell and routing`).\n\nOne repo-local limit showed up during browser QA: the backend currently fails to boot because local config/secrets include unsupported keys, so the shell was visually verified in its offline-fallback state. That is documented in the summary file.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 161, "prompt_index": 21, "prompt_name": "20 \u2014 Frontend App Shell and Routing", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T01:25:40-07:00"}
{"color": "bright_black", "emoji": "\u2753", "event_type": "Unkown Event", "message": "{ \"item\": { \"id\": \"item_29\", \"items\": [ { \"completed\": true, \"text\": \"Inspect the current frontend shell, routing, and verification tooling to align the new structure with existing patterns.\" }, { \"completed\": false, \"text\": \"Implement t...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_29", "items": [{"completed": true, "text": "Inspect the current frontend shell, routing, and verification tooling to align the new structure with existing patterns."}, {"completed": false, "text": "Implement the app shell, route configuration, page modules, and folder-structure conventions for pages, shared UI, hooks, API clients, and state stores."}, {"completed": false, "text": "Add or update automated tests and run lint/build/test plus browser-based route verification with screenshots."}, {"completed": false, "text": "Commit the implemented code changes, then write the required detailed markdown summary file as the final action."}], "type": "todo_list"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 162, "prompt_index": 21, "prompt_name": "20 \u2014 Frontend App Shell and Routing", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T01:25:40-07:00"}
